Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
auto_file_dir(25.10)                                      auto_file_dir(25.10)

Name
       auto_file_dir

Syntax
       auto_file_dir <directoryName>

       Type: String

       Default: ./

       Specifies the directory to store files/sub-directories 'auto-generated'
       by  the tool. This includes report files or other output files with de-
       fault names that are automatically created by some commands in the cur-
       rent run directory. Default names that have been overridden with a name
       chosen by the user, are not affected. This allows multiple simultaneous
       runs from the same run directory to direct output  files  to  different
       result directories to avoid collisions.

Related Information
              * auto_file_prefix

